snippet.title: STREAM PAIRS | The memory matching game to play ON YOUR LIVE STREAM
snippet.description:
PLAY NOW WITH YOUR AUDIENCE! 
https://streampairs.com 

Stream Pairs is a memory matching game made to be played with your audience on your live stream! All you need is the chat to send the answers.
It's easy to set up, and you pay NOTHING for it — the best option to add more fun and engagement to your live stream.

Find more stream games at https://onrizon.tv. 
Give power to your chat and join the #playersnotviewers movement!
